CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 15, 1963, pg. 12, reads: "Grandmother Feted - Little Robin Bullard poses here with her grandmother, Mrs. Margaret Bullard, after the little girl feted her grandmother with a birthday party at 2901 Bedford Ave. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Margaret Bullard wearing striped party hat, holding her granddaughter Robin Bullard over sheet cake inscribed "Happy Birthday Peg" in kitchen, for birthday party of Margaret Bullard, 2801 Bedford Avenue
